1.question: What is the Open-Source AI Tool Directory?
1.answer: The AI Tool Directory - tap4.ai is building an AI tool directory to help you get your favorite AI tools. You can find AI writing tools, AI marketing tools, AI rewriting tools, AI SEO tools, AI learning tools, AI generation tools, AI research tools, AI art tools, AI music tools, AI video tools, AI coding tools, AI image tools, and more.

2.question: How to find your AI tool in the AI Tool Directory?
2.answer-2: 2. Browse AI tools in the AI Tool Directory
2.answer-3: 3. Click on the AI tool you need, view details and access it

3.question: What are the main features of the AI Tool Directory?
3.answer-1: 1. Free AI Tool Directory: Find your favorite AI tools for free
3.answer-2: 2. Startup Company List: Free startup company list for AI tool developers

4.question: Is submitting an AI tool to the AI Tool Directory free?
4.answer: Yes, it's free for now. But you should share the reverse link of the AI Tool Directory!

5.question: What types of AI tools does the AI Tool Directory support?
5.answer: We will support all types of AI tools soon. Please wait for a few days.

6.question: How often is the AI tool list updated in the AI Tool Directory?
6.answer: The AI tool list will be updated daily.

7.question: Does the AI Tool Directory support GPT-4o or Sora AI?
7.answer: You can get GPT-4o or Sora AI tools here. There are introductions to GPT-4o and Sora video tools, and you can access the tool's website.

8.question: Troubleshooting
8.answer: If the content doesn't appear, try using another browser, clear the cache. If the problem still exists, please contact us: mapleshaw@gmail.com

9.question: How is the content of the AI Tool Directory generated?
9.answer: The description content of AI tools is generated by Anthropic's Claude.

10.question: What are the usage rights of AI tools?
10.answer: The AI Tool Directory is just a directory of AI tools. The usage rights of AI tools are based on the website of the AI tool.

11.question: Is the Web UI of the AI Tool Directory open-source?
11.answer: Yes, we will open-source the Web UI of the AI Tool Directory on GitHub (https://github.com/6677-ai/tap4-ai-webui). Please give us a star.

privacyPolicy.1-h1: Open-Source AI Tool Directory Privacy Policy

We collect personal information to provide and improve our service. Unless otherwise stated in this privacy policy, we will not share your information with anyone.
privacyPolicy.2-p: To provide better service, we may request certain personally identifiable information when you use our service. The information we request will be stored on your device, and we will not collect it in any way. This application uses third-party services that may collect information used to identify you.
privacyPolicy.3-p: I want to inform you that every time you use our service, we collect data and information (through third-party products) in the event of an error in the application. This log data may include your device's IP address, device name, operating system version, configuration, and other statistics information.
privacyPolicy.4-p: Cookies are files with small amounts of data that are commonly used as anonymous unique identifiers. These files are sent to your browser from the website you visit and are stored on your device's internal memory. This service does not use these 'cookies' explicitly. However, the application may use third-party code and libraries that use 'cookies' to collect information and improve their service.
privacyPolicy.5-p-1: We may employ third-party companies and individuals due to the following reasons:
privacyPolicy.5-li-2: To provide service on our behalf;
privacyPolicy.5-li-3: To perform services related to our service;

privacyPolicy.5-p-2: I want to inform users of this service that these third parties have access to your personal information. The reason is to perform the tasks assigned to them on our behalf. However, they are obligated not to disclose or use the information for any other purpose.
privacyPolicy.6-p: I value the trust you place in us by providing your personal information, so we are committed to using commercially acceptable means to protect it. But please remember that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure and reliable, and I cannot guarantee its absolute security.
privacyPolicy.7-p: This service may contain links to other sites. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that site. Note that these external sites are not operated by us. Therefore, I strongly advise you to review the privacy policies of these websites. I have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.
privacyPolicy.8-p: I may update our privacy policy from time to time. Thus, I advise you to review this page periodically for any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page. These changes are effective as soon as they are posted on this page.
